titles.title: You Are Not a god created

properties.verseOrder: v1 c1 v2 c1 b1 c1 b1 e1

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
A
You are not a god created
By human hands
You are not a god dependent
On any mortal man
You are not a god in need of
Anything we can give
By Your plan
That's just the way it is (repeat)

verse.name: c1
verse.lines:
You are God alone
From before time began
You were on Your throne
You are God alone
And right now
In the good times and bad
You are on Your throne
You are God alone

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
You're the only God whose power
None can contend
You're the only God whose name
And praise will never end
You're the only God who's worthy
Of everything we can give
You are God
That's just the way it is

verse.name: b1
verse.lines:
You're unchangeable
You're unshakable
You're unstoppable
That's what you are x2

verse.name: e1
verse.lines:
And right now
In the good times and bad
You are on Your throne
You are God alone
